        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer782941" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1311061079863789247">This book inspired a major paradigm shift for me. Shortly after reading it, I enrolled in acupuncture school, and life has not been the same, will never be the same. I have to reread this book every so often for its crucial reminder: that nonviolence can work and must work and will work to change the world...but we also have to work...we need to heal ourselves and others. I highly recommend this book.</span>

          </span>
