          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Audible Audio " href="/book/show/34445844-the-fifth-sacred-thing">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2230615-kristen?shelf=audio">audio</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/2230615-kristen?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>
