              <span id="reviewTextContainer2263067611" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1714020927672937766">I loved this story of a near future utopia based on the principles of earth based spirituality and social justice. The combination of the well thought out details of how daily life would look in a post-capitalist society, combined with the rich description of the various locations across California where I grew up, made for an emotional read for me. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


